properties.headline: NSW Health Vaccination Centre - SYDNEY OLYMPIC PARK Figtree Drive at Australia Avenue
properties.publicTransport: Plan your trip by public transport at transportnsw.info.

arrangementAttachments.displayName: Sydney Olympic Park NSW Health Vaccination Centre – transport and parking map
arrangementAttachments.linkName: Sydney Olympic Park NSW Health Vaccination Centre – transport and parking map

properties.otherAdvice:
The NSW Health Vaccination Centre in Sydney Olympic Park is located at 1 Figtree Drive. The centre is in operation for those with confirmed appointments only from 8am to 8pm daily Monday to Saturday and from 9am to 4pm on Sundays. 

Nearby parking is available at P3 car park on Sarah Durack Ave. Follow signage to walk to the centre, or catch the shuttle bus.

Allow additional travel time on roads approaching the precinct including Australia Ave, Underwood Rd and Hill Rd, particularly during the morning and evening peak periods.

For more information about the COVID-19 Vaccination Program in NSW or to check your eligibility and make a booking, visit the NSW Health website at health.nsw.gov.au/COVID-19.

The NSW Health Vaccination Centre in Belmont is located at the former Bunnings site at 393 Pacific Hwy. The centre is in operation for those with confirmed appointments only from 8am to 8pm daily Monday to Friday, and from 8am to 4.30pm on Saturday and Sunday. 

Allow additional travel time on roads approaching the precinct particularly during the morning and evening peak. 

For more information about the COVID-19 Vaccination Program in NSW or to check your eligibility and make a booking, visit the NSW Health website at health.nsw.gov.au/COVID-19.
